metadata.name: BYOCassette: Amazonia Soundtrack
metadata.description:
BYOCassettes are the genesis music NFTs of the BYOVerse. These rare collectibles unlock exclusive soundtracks in-game that will transport you deeper into the game world and immerse you in the full gameplay experience.

The original BYOVerse soundtrack consists of 16 unique tracks, each representing its respective biome. Every BYOLand holder who made the snapshot on 7/17/2022 & 1/11/2023 was eligible to claim 1 BYOCassette for each biome they own.

Download the full soundtrack here: https://byocassette-amazonia.lostboy.io/

Ownership of these collectibles grant you full commercial rights to the Art and Music of the NFT.

Produced by and in partnership with [LOSTBOY](https://opensea.io/collection/lostboy-nft).
